A"}, {"file_name": "Pythagoras_02.png", "id": "1521857538609718", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/65402154_1521857545276384_6932935515601424484_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=g-MmEObd92oQ7kNvgE3G71v&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBra4kY2gk8ZV2J8_SpOxcpxk-umcNIQtZhwx0TY9JkmQ&oe=6762B45C"}, {"file_name": "Levy_02.png", "id": "196149426884252", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/43997710_196149430217585_1332548403471429223_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=bGDtxAeJtgIQ7kNvgE7qg34&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAsJPi4N-DzCrewQi9mtBc7DUOXF7f-DCPP3UDxEF6o9w&oe=6762A31B"}, {"file_name": "Radial_Solid.png", "id": "271501478838543", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031373_271501482171876_8031340628965781426_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1Y0lE8_YUCIQ7kNvgGTDmnO&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDYJH7b58D8PMB43mLQZ3ZHrogXOWIKmCs1yD3Xh_mJDg&oe=67629D5B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Psydmind_Landscape_2560x1440.png", "id": "1020482742612505", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982514_1020482745945838_6452784102981224285_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4G9ncEdygQsQ7kNvgFt7k4D&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDDVC0Y_naY33Uc6bxIuR_-xr-kHE4pcFzAKcpTkNk7vA&oe=6762B4DB"}, "display_name": "VoctoR PsydMind (Clinical Research)", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Experience the transformative power of VR meditation with PsydMind, your personal gateway to inner peace and well-being.\n\nPsydMind offers a powerful approach to meditation: \nFive distinct categories: Each scene is designed to address a specific mental health concern, incorporating elements of color theory, math, and shape theory to optimize your experience.\nGenerative art: Witness the mesmerizing beauty of evolving fractal landscapes, created through generative art, adding a dynamic and captivating element to your meditation practice.\nObject movement with binaural beats: Harmonize your brainwaves with the gentle movement of objects and the soothing sounds of binaural beats, promoting a deeper state of relaxation and focus.\n\nData collection and analysis: Gain insights into your progress and identify areas for improvement through anonymous data collection and analysis.\nBinaural beats: Incorporating beats with the moving objects could further promote relaxation and focus, aligning with the user's desired mental state.\nMusic: Carefully selected music can complement the visuals and binaural beats, creating a harmonious and immersive experience.\n\nAreas for further exploration:\nCustomizable parameters: Consider allowing users to adjust the parameters of the fractal drawings, binaural beats, and music to personalize their experience.\nIntegration with other tools: Investigate potential integration with other wellness apps or wearable devices to offer a more holistic approach to mental", "short_description": "Experience the transformative power of VR meditation with PsydMind, your personal gateway to inner peace and well-being.\nCombining the five categories of scenes (anxiety, stress, ADHD, insomnia, and depression) with design principles like fractal drawing using generative art sounds like a powerful and creative approach. Objects moving with binaural beats and music further enhances the immersive and therapeutic experience."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://iottech.com.tr/policy/psydmind-privacypolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://iottech.com.tr/policy/psydmind-termsservice.html", "publisher_name": "RevinoLabs", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.iottech.com.tr/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, 