8838543", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031373_271501482171876_8031340628965781426_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1Y0lE8_YUCIQ7kNvgGTDmnO&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDYJH7b58D8PMB43mLQZ3ZHrogXOWIKmCs1yD3Xh_mJDg&oe=67629D5B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Psydmind_Landscape_2560x1440.png", "id": "1020482742612505", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982514_1020482745945838_6452784102981224285_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=4G9ncEdygQsQ7kNvgFt7k4D&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDDVC0Y_naY33Uc6bxIuR_-xr-kHE4pcFzAKcpTkNk7vA&oe=6762B4DB"}, "display_name": "VoctoR PsydMind", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Experience the transformative power of VR meditation with PsydMind, your personal gateway to inner peace and well-being.\n\nPsydMind offers a powerful approach to meditation: \nFive distinct categories: Each scene is designed to address a specific mental health concern, incorporating elements of color theory, math, and shape theory to optimize your experience.\nGenerative art: Witness the mesmerizing beauty of evolving fractal landscapes, created through generative art, adding a dynamic and captivating element to your meditation practice.\nObject movement with binaural beats: Harmonize your brainwaves with the gentle movement of objects and the soothing sounds of binaural beats, promoting a deeper state of relaxation and focus.\n\nData collection and analysis: Gain insights into your progress and identify areas for improvement through anonymous data collection and analysis.\nBinaural beats: Incorporating beats with the moving objects could further promote relaxation and focus, aligning with the user's desired mental state.\nMusic: Carefully selected music can complement the visuals and binaural beats, creating a harmonious and immersive experience.\n\nAreas for further exploration:\nCustomizable parameters: Consider allowing users to adjust the parameters of the fractal drawings, binaural beats, and music to personalize their experience.\nIntegration with other tools: Investigate potential integration with other wellness apps or wearable devices to offer a more holistic approach to mental", "short_description": "Experience the transformative power of VR meditation with PsydMind, your personal gateway to inner peace and well-being.\nCombining the five categories of scenes (anxiety, stress, ADHD, insomnia, and depression) with design principles like fractal drawing using generative art sounds like a powerful and creative approach. Objects moving with binaural beats and music further enhances the immersive and therapeutic experience."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://iottech.com.tr/policy/psydmind-privacypolicy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://iottech.com.tr/policy/psydmind-termsservice.html", "publisher_name": "RevinoLabs", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.iottech.com.tr/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "810139357995560"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": null, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "6480979042012273"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "2041415516221064"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "2041415516221064"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1701797496, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "